  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7740804">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7740804/" class="title-link">精彩的分析</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7740804"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2954191/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2954191-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2954191/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">赛百浪子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-18"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-18 21:39:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7740804_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          与其姊妹篇≪经略幽燕≫比较，作者在史料的运用和辨识上似乎更为驾轻就熟，动辄搬出理论术语的情况大为减少，更多的是深入的分析和出色的考证，虽然缺少地图，作者的学术功底和才华仍得以尽情地展现。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7740804_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7740804_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





